http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title.value: Rhode Island K-12 Grade Span Expectations in the Arts - Dance

http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: The Rhode Island K-12 Grade Span Expectations in the Arts, has been developed as a means to identify the arts concepts and skills expected of all students. The RI arts GSEs encompass the content eligible for inclusion in local assessment in the arts in grades K - 12. They are not intended to represent the full arts curriculum at each grade span, but are meant to capture the "major ideas" of the art forms that can be assessed. The goal is that the arts GSEs focus the curriculum, but do not restrict it.
